snippet.textDisplay: Mehhh....Color by numbers amalgamation of "Been there, Done that" tropes. It sounds like a bunch of pieces of different songs that have been taped together with discount price stickers pulled from the unsold back stock of her last 10 years' worth of worthless records. Typical of Pop assembly line drive though producers to think that's going to work, however, much like a body with an organ transplant, the host has to accept the new appendage for actual LIFE to be maintained and in the case of Lady Ga Ga, she should get a refund from whatever she paid her Luciferian bros (If they haven't ditched her yet) to steal this kidney. Because the patient is rejecting the transplant, and so soon will the public...Lazy songwriting as far as what her contributions might have been, lyrics don't rhyme, aren't in the least bit clever, title and theme seem like an invitation to go "InTeNeTZ" on her, the video? She looks like some dime store Lady Ga Ga tribute band, costumes come off as silly in an attempt to look interesting, the dancing is embarrassing at times...lame at others...This is what the feebleminded eater/breeders of today call....."Epic failz?"......Almost as embarrassing as that pathetically miscalculated "A Star is Born" debacle.....siiiiigh....Well, Lady Ga Ga, you reap what you sow, and you haven't even BEGUN to pay the price for knowingly and with malice of forethought pushing Luciferianism on children, when that "payback" catches up with it's "bitch" I wouldn't want to be standing next to her, there is such a thing as right and wrong kiddies, that may be a shock if you grew up with the likes of Ga Ga trying to convince you down was up and up was left, but if you want to know why you feel depressed, anxious, meaningless, having evil pushed down your throat from a young age certainly had a lot to do with it, those who want to recover...re-educate yourselves, and understand you've been mind-F&^ked by evil people, take everything you THOUGHT you knew and flush it...then start thinking about right and wrong as inherent spiritual truths, and how humility and uncredited love are the way to salvation, beware the "Fame Monsters" there is not a single one of them who isn't looking to feast on your remains, no ONE, TURN OFF THE IPHONE and do something nice for somebody, then do it again...and again (Without turning the Iphone back on)...As for Ga Ga, well, she comes from a school that says "Take, step on, there's no right or wrong, just rich or broke, famous or nobody, strong or weak....so she set out to take and be the richest, most famous "Somebody" she could be....she should have realized that in the predators world you can't be the Apex without killing your predecessor, as the Sith in Star Wars, you want to be the Sith Lord.....coolio...all you gotta do is take out your Master and hope he taught you everything he knew. Or in Pro-Wrestling terms "To be the man, you gotta beat the man WOOOOOOOOOOOOO!" Lady Ga Ga was under the delusion that with all her success, she could just "Ignore the man" and they would fade off into the sunset.....Unfortunately for her Madonna has been playing this game for a long, long time, and has been taking out rivals since 1983 when Cyndi Lauper was "Marked for death" at the MTV video awards. Lauper was a worldwide sensation in 83 (And she's so unusual is still 100 x better than anything Maddona ever did) she was as big as big got, three years later...DROPPED by her label "Yeah, sorry, you're too old, we're moving on) Lady Ga Ga was naive to think she was going to steal the crown off the Queen bitch's head....You BETTER BELIEVE Madonna has used every resource available to her to ensure Gaga does little but embarrass herself for the rest of her public life...and from the looks of things...she's doing a GREAT JOB.
